title: AMAZING VIEWS FULLY FURNISHED IN ONE PARAISO!!!
posting_body: ['AMAZING BAY VIEWS!!!FURNISHED 3BED/3BATHROOMS AND 1 GUEST, located at Edgewater, Miami’s hottest new neighborhood.', 'Top of the line appliances, custom made closets ,Miami’s hottest new neighborhood.', 'It features a private elevator/foyer.', 'Top of the line appliances, custom made closets and luxurious master bath with dual sink vanity, shower and tub.', 'One Paraiso is a chic contemporary high-rise condominium with a private beach club, private tennis courts, two pools, jacuzzi, kids playroom, theater, spa and fitness center.', 'Minutes away from Midtown, the Design District, Wynwood, Miami Beach and Downtown.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
